              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Spectroscopically pure (99.99%) terbium foils of",
                "thickness 20.6 mg/cm2. The samples were cut into pieces",
                "of 1.2x1.2cm2 and glued on aluminium frame of size",
                "3.0x2.5cm2 having a circular hole of diam. 8 mm in",
                "its center. The aluminium foils were also inserted in",
                "the stack, which acts as energy degraders"
